Road segments in Lisbon

Source: R/data.R
lisbon_road_segments.Rd

A dataset representing road segments in Lisbon, with X, Y and Z (elevation) dimensions for each coordinate.

lisbon_road_segments

Format

And object of class sf

Source

Produced by ESRI's 3D Analyst extension

Examples

names(lisbon_road_segments)
#>  [1] "OBJECTID"   "fid_1"      "gradient_s" "Shape_Leng" "Z_Min"     
#>  [6] "Z_Max"      "Z_Mean"     "SLength"    "Min_Slope"  "Max_Slope" 
#> [11] "Avg_Slope"  "z0"         "z1"         "gradverifi" "query"     
#> [16] "lat"        "lon"        "lat_min"    "lat_max"    "lon_min"   
#> [21] "lon_max"    "bbox"       "geom"      
plot(lisbon_road_segments["Avg_Slope"])
